OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2023FDuring ITV's coverage of King
OL,7,FCharles III's coronation, actress Adjoa
OL,8,FAndoh commented that the balcony of
OL,9,FBuckingham Palace looked "terribly
OL,10,Fwhite". Ofcom received 8,421 complaints
OL,11,Fabout the comment - the 10th-highest
OL,12,Ffigure since 2004. The comment was
OL,13,Fassessed but not pursued.
